Eskom Doesn’t Have Time For ‘Sufficient’ Maintenance Before Winter Starts

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-04-08T09:39:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/eskom-doesn-t-have-time-for-sufficient-maintenance-before-winter-starts.html
Eskom Holdings Ltd.,  South Africa ’s
state-owned power utility, doesn’t have enough time to complete
“sufficient” plant maintenance in the run-up to winter in the
southern hemisphere, Public Enterprises Minister Malusi Gigaba
said in a speech in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
